       (DEFAULT_DATABASE EQUAL default_database=id)? (DEFAULT_LANGUAGE EQUAL default_laguage=id)?  
       (NAME EQUAL login_name=id)? (CHECK_POLICY EQUAL (ON|OFF) )? (CHECK_EXPIRATION EQUAL (ON|OFF) )? 
